title: ArtyTorrent Pack 91-Tech Trance Drum Loops 140-149bpm-WAV
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 91-Tech Trance Drum Loops 140-149bpm-WAV
---------------------------------------------------------

Miscellaneous drum loops for techno, hard house and psytrance, including many samples created by Carl Cox and BT.
Tempo ranges from 140-149 bpm.

Torrent contains 4 RAR files with 113 loops
-------------------------------------------
Ejay Tech 140 (45 loops)
Kick Loops 140-149 (24)
Misc Tech Trance 140-149 (38)
Overdrive 140 (6)

Samples are from a wide variety of sources including CDs by EastWest, Sony/Sonic Foundry, and Loopology/Syntrillium, and have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.

More loops in this tempo range will be posted soon, so get ready for some more breaks, electro and funky rock loops.
